'''''The Great Kimberley Diamond Robbery'''''( '''Die Groot Diamantroof van Kimberley''' ), na none mu ikinamico nka '''The Star of the South''', ni filime yo mu 1911 yo muri Afurika y'Epfo y'Abirabura n'umweru byicecekeye iyobowe na RCE Nissen kandi ikorwa na Rufe Naylor muri sosiyete ya Springbok.   Iyi niyo filime yambere yikinamico yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo mumateka ya sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.  
